original: Lonander, Brita Maria, tandläkare, Sävedalen, f. 2/11/13 i Gbg av bygg-mäst. Emil L. o. Elisabeth Nilsson. — Stud:ex. v. Gbgs h. a. 1. f. fl. 33, tand-l:kand. 34, tandl. 37. Vik. i Gbg 38, assist, i Vänersborg s. å., dislr:tandl. i Lerum 42-44, egen prakt, i Sävedalen v. Gbg sed. 44.
translated: Lonander, Brita Maria, dentist, Sävedalen, born on 2/11/13 in Gothenburg to master builder Emil L. and Elisabeth Nilsson. — Received High School Diploma from Gothenburg's Higher Education Institution in 1933, completed dental studies in 1934, became a dentist in 1937. Worked temporarily in Gothenburg in 1938, as an assistant in Vänersborg the same year, and as a district dentist in Lerum from 1942 to 1944. Started her own dental practice in Sävedalen near Gothenburg in 1944.
